Ensuring that the team follows the Agile principles and practices

Leading and facilitating sprint planning, daily stand-up, sprint review, and sprint retrospective meetings

Coaching and mentoring team members and product owner on Agile values and principles

Resolving any issues or impediments that arise and removing roadblocks that could hamper the team’s productivity

Monitoring the team’s progress and ensuring quality and timeliness of deliverables

Promoting continuous improvement and collaboration within the team and the organization